data.description: Discover the beauty of this two-story, 4 bed, 2.5 bath home in Spring, Texas. Recently upgraded with Renewal by Anderson energy efficient windows (June 2021), this residence offers a blend of style and functionality. The main level presents with a welcoming living room with a wood burning fireplace, a separate dining room, and a kitchen equipped with a breakfast bar and eat-in area. Upstairs, you'll find four spacious bedrooms, including a large primary bedroom and ensuite bathroom with 2 closets. The exterior features a detached garage and large fully fenced backyard, ideal for outdoor activities. This home provides a comfortable and inviting living space for you and your family. You do not want to miss this opportunity!
